{"tid":1230051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"免費法律支援+LEGAL ADVICE  - 星火同盟","createTime":"2019-06-16T05:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T10:32:58.000Z","uid":53666,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6e89a750533af6138319d5950be8284bb8c01ac8","tid":1230051,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:56:54.000Z","msg":"6。16【遊行街站義務法律咨詢】<br />\n<br />\n星火同盟今日會於 616遊行路線途中開設街站，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屆時會有多位義務律師在場，解答各位同道的法律問題。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n若你在6月9日大遊行，或6月12日金鐘衝突期間，曾經被捕、被警員要求記錄身份證號碼，又或是有其他相關法律問題，屆時歡迎到我們的街站向義務律師查詢。他們<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">分別來自處理過暴動、煽惑暴動及非法集結等案件的律師事務所，擁有豐富經驗，</span></strong>衷心希望能夠幫助大家。<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年6月16日（星期日）<br />\n時間：下午3時至6時半<br />\n地點：灣仔港鐵站 家計會門前<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://oi68.tinypic.com/ossojp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Foi68.tinypic.com%2Fossojp.jpg&h=0a9450fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34af15ceda60e5508728466a244eb03ed2906e2e","tid":1230051,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:58:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/photos/a.1989972677956521/2481788242108293/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2Fphotos%2Fa.1989972677956521%2F2481788242108293%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WP5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=fb06812a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/photos/a.1989972677956521/2481788242108293/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\nFrom SparkallianceHK FB Page"},{"pid":"983281689aa900de78846d530cd80970551a07cd","tid":1230051,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:58:40.000Z","msg":"推比更多人知<br />\n要做智慧型市民呀大家!!!"},{"pid":"929f4bdacd7e443f09c92fd77ec1716c2c722a1d","tid":1230051,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-